This field could be used for making notes about what they changed in this shot so that the director or lead can know what parts of the shot to pay attention to, and so you can remember what was changed after it goes into an edit. This is a long field that has multiple lines of text to show multi-line handling. If the comment field is left empty on the job then this will not be visible.

You can even use Shift+Enter to create multiple lines.
